Website for Kaizen Yelp
http://kaizenyelp.com:8001/kaizen


1.	Goto kaizen yelp website.
2.	Create an account with your name, password and email id.
3.	Login with the username and password.
4.	Search for any category , city with your preferences.
5.	A list of businesses would be displayed based on the search criteria.
6.	Click on any of the business details button to get the particulars  of that business
7.	All the details of the business would be displayed along with the location in Google maps.
8.	
9.	Click on Subscribe button to subscribe to that business.
10.	You would get an email for confirming the subscription from AWS.
11.	If any other user publishes a review to the same business , the subscribed user would get an email regarding the review.
12.	In the business details page , click on the Coupons button
13.	All the coupons available for that business in the selected area within the 20 miles radius would be displayed.

Yelp Dataset is limited to Arizona , so we are providing some of the search criteria.
Here are some of the search criteria 



Category	City
Italian	Scottsdale
Chinese	Phoenix 
Sandwiches	Mesa
Mexican	Buckeye
Korean	Chandler
Indian	Tempe
Tattoo	Glendale
Automotive	Scottsdale
Pets	Glendale

